---
import Container from "@/components/layout/Container.astro";
import Section from "@/components/layout/Section.astro";
import LinkButton from "@/components/ui/LinkButton.astro";
---

<Section background="inverse">
  <Container>
    <div class="cta-header">
      <h2 class="cta-title">Contact</h2>
      <span class="cta-subtitle">문의하기</span>
    </div>
    <p class="cta-text">
      견적 문의, 상담, 샘플 요청 등 무엇이든 편하게 문의해 주세요.
    </p>
    <ul class="cta-list">
      <li class="cta-list-item">
        책자, 카탈로그, 브로슈어 인쇄를 의뢰하고 싶다
      </li>
      <li class="cta-list-item">대량 인쇄 견적을 받고 싶다</li>
      <li class="cta-list-item">용지 선택이나 후가공에 대해 상담하고 싶다</li>
      <li class="cta-list-item">납기 일정을 확인하고 싶다</li>
      <li class="cta-list-item">용지 샘플을 받아보고 싶다 등</li>
    </ul>
    <div class="cta-actions">
      <LinkButton href="/contact" variant="solid-sub" size="large">
        문의하기
      </LinkButton>
    </div>
  </Container>
</Section>

<style lang="scss">
  .cta-header {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--sp-xs);

    @media (min-width: 900px) {
      gap: var(--sp-sm);
    }
  }

  .cta-title {
    color: var(--c-text-inverse);
    font-size: clamp(var(--fs-2xl), 5vw, var(--fs-3xl));
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: var(--lh-none);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .cta-subtitle {
    color: var(--c-text-inverse-sub);
    font-size: var(--fs-sm);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: var(--lh-normal);

    @media (min-width: 900px) {
      font-size: var(--fs-base);
    }
  }

  .cta-text {
    margin: var(--sp-xl) 0;
    color: var(--c-text-inverse-lightest);
    font-size: var(--fs-base);
    line-height: var(--lh-loose);

    @media (min-width: 900px) {
      font-size: var(--fs-md);
    }
  }

  .cta-list {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--sp-sm);
    color: var(--c-text-inverse-lighter);
    font-size: var(--fs-sm);
    line-height: var(--lh-relaxed);

    @media (min-width: 600px) {
      font-size: var(--fs-base);
    }

    @media (min-width: 900px) {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }

  .cta-list-item {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: var(--sp-lg);
    text-align: left;

    &::before {
      content: "・";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
    }

    &:first-child {
      margin: 0;
    }
  }

  .cta-actions {
    margin-top: var(--sp-2xl);
  }
</style>
